name: 马修·琼斯
introduction: Matthew Jones is a Chicago-born and trained actor who has appeared in nearly 70 different television shows and motion pictures at the Guest Star or Co-Star level, including Yellowstone, S.W.A.T., Curb Your Enthusiasm, N.C.I.S. (Vegas, L.A. and New Orleans), General Hospital(30 episodes), It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia, Brooklyn Nine-Nine, and so many more. Films include science fiction blockbuster Ad Astra, and action drama Break. Matthew can also be a local hire in the city of Chicago.
